application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Outline application for a mixed use redevelopment of existing timber yard site to provide up to 6,390sqm of business units (use classes B1, B2 or B8); up to 2,710sqm of business units (use class B1 only); 48,883sqm of residential floorspace (not more than 613 units); 7,096sqm of live/work space (not more than 69 units); up to 560sqm of community facilities; up to 220sqm of retail space (A1); up to 500sqm of bar/cafe/restaurant space (A3); up to 581 car parking spaces; and publicly accessible open space.
